  contentShort: Rebranding!
  content: "Due to unforeseen circumstances, the head of TOAEIPE, previously known
    as the league of labour, was forced to resign.\n\nBut this is an opportunity
    for a new beginning! \n\nWe are happy to introduce: The Unofficial Department
    against  Worker rights. Or short TUDAWR! "
